# Midwestern Brand Application

This folder powers the `midwestern-brand-application` Claude skill.

## Structure
- `midwestern-design-system.md` — Foundation file. Applied to all output types.
- `formats/` — Format-specific guidelines. Each file covers one output type.

## Adding a new format
1. Create a new file in `formats/` named `mw-[format].md` (e.g. `mw-proposals.md`)
2. Follow the same structure as existing format files
3. The Claude skill will pick it up automatically — no other changes needed
